{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6d5c15e07cb4b1e130864611285\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-06-08 17:04 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"1ed3af67","parentId":"5a029e7f","timestamp":"2026-06-08T09:05:01.197Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"b01ab3d8","parentId":"1ed3af67","timestamp":"2026-06-08T09:05:06.887Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (Yousan/叶枝君, the owner) is asking me to summarize the workflow for updating the test server (更新测试服). This is documented in my TOOLS.md and MEMORY.md. Let me provide a clear summary.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，更新测试服的工作流如下：\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 更新测试服工作流\n\n### 本质\nUnity 客户端热更流水线，更新客户端资源/代码到 CDN。\n\n### 完整步骤\n\n1. **前置检查**\n   - 检查是否有 Unity 进程在执行 `RunHotUpdatePipeline`（防止重复执行）\n   - 杀掉所有 Unity Editor 进程（避免项目被占用）\n\n2. **Git 手动更新**\n   - `git pull` 更新主工程 `E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon` 当前分支\n   - 遍历所有子模块，检查 detached HEAD 状态\n   - 修复 detached HEAD → 切回正确分支 → `git pull`\n\n3. **运行 Unity 流水线**\n   - 执行 `RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat`\n   - Unity batch mode 运行 `BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline`\n   - **默认增量构建**（不清 Bundles 缓存，速度快）\n\n4. **编译结果检查**\n   - Unity 退出码 0 **不代表完全成功**，必须扫日志：\n     ```\n     BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\n     ```\n   - 检查关键字：`error CS\\d+:`（C#编译报错）、`git更新失败`、`Build completed with.*errors`\n\n5. **通知**\n   - ✅ **成功** → 在「月圆之夜CCG开发群」@ 兵王（周以天）\n   - ❌ **失败** → 只私聊通知主人，**不在群里发失败消息**\n\n### 分流机制\n- 主 agent 做完前置检查和 git 更新后，**开子 session** 去跑 Unity 流水线\n- 主 session 立即释放，保持响应能力\n- 子 session 完成后自动汇报结果\n\n### 快捷手动命令\n```powershell\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\tools\\hotupdate-scripts\\UpdateTestServer.ps1\"\n```\n\n或者直接跑 bat：\n```\nE:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\n```\n\n---\n\n就这些，需要我跑一次吗？🌸"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":19880,"output":523,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20403,"cost":{"input":0.0027832,"output":0.00014644000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00292964}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780909501197,"responseId":"0c77d10b-1f5d-47c7-b9af-fc34ebe39590"}}
